OL,3,CNuclear fusion reactor celebrates 40
OL,4,Cyears of pioneering scientific finds
OL,6,FScientists hope nuclear fusion, a
OL,7,Fprocess that powers the sun, could be
OL,8,Four main source of energy within the
OL,9,Fnext half century.
OL,11,FThis reactor in has been at the
OL,12,Fforefront of groundbreaking - and
OL,13,Frecord-breaking experiments - to find
OL,14,Fcleaner ways of powering our planet.
OL,16,FBorn out of the oil crisis in the
OL,17,F1970s and the need for western
OL,18,Fgovernments to move away from fossil
OL,19,Ffuels, the research facility into
OL,20,Fnuclear fusion began in earnest in
OL,21,F1984.
