OL,3,CNuclear fusion reactor celebrates 40
OL,4,Cyears of pioneering scientific finds
OL,6,FAnd ever since, it's been record after
OL,7,Frecord being broken. World first and
OL,8,Fgroundbreaking vital science tucked
OL,9,Faway in the Oxfordshire countryside.
OL,11,FA recent record broken by the team at
OL,12,FJET (Joint European Torus) facility,
OL,13,Fcomes at a time of change.
OL,15,FThis is because after more than 40
OL,16,Fyears, the decades' long work of some
OL,17,Fof the best scientists in the world,
OL,18,Fis coming to an end.
