OL,3,CNuclear fusion reactor celebrates 40
OL,4,Cyears of pioneering scientific finds
OL,6,FBut decommissioning a nuclear fusion
OL,7,Freactor is not a simple task and it
OL,8,Fhas never been done in the world
OL,9,Fbefore.
OL,11,FThe team at Culham - once again, at
OL,12,Fthe forefront of learning about this
OL,13,Ftechnology for the rest of the world
OL,14,Fto use too - in their own reactors.
OL,16,FTaking apart the machine will "all be
OL,17,Fdone with robots" said the CEO of UK
OL,18,FAtomic Energy Authority professor Sir
OL,19,FJim Chapman.
