OL,3,CNuclear fusion reactor celebrates 40
OL,4,Cyears of pioneering scientific finds
OL,6,F"There's four tonnes of metal, all
OL,7,Fdisassembled robotically and then we
OL,8,Ftake apart the vessel itself," Chapman
OL,9,Fremarked.
OL,11,FThey will also capture the fuel which
OL,12,Fis embedded in the metal and capture
OL,13,Fit back - to reuse it to not waste any
OL,14,Fvital energy.
OL,16,FI got a tour of their robotic lab,
OL,17,Fwhich showed several scientists
OL,18,Fworking together with a person
OL,19,Fphysically moving the robot inside the
OL,20,Fmachine.
