OL,6,FThe painstaking process will take
OL,7,Fyears in order to remove the inner
OL,8,Fparts.
OL,10,FA full decommission is a long way
OL,11,Faway, possibly in the next 15 years.
OL,13,FIt is widely appreciated any future
OL,14,Fsteps towards a full commercial
OL,15,Freactor wouldn't have come anywhere
OL,16,Fnear a possibility without the work in
OL,17,FCulham.
